This project includes several third‑party components. The following
libraries and tools are bundled in the Docker image, each with its own
license.

* **Arduino CLI** – Apache License 2.0
  <https://github.com/arduino/arduino-cli/blob/master/LICENSE>
* **Raspberry Pi Pico SDK** – BSD 3‑Clause "New" or "Revised" License
  <https://github.com/raspberrypi/pico-sdk/blob/master/LICENSE>
* **OpenAI Python SDK** – Apache License 2.0
  <https://github.com/openai/openai-python/blob/main/LICENSE>
* **Bash** – GNU GPLv3 (the executable bundled with Debian)
  <https://gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt>
* **Docker CE CLI** – Apache License 2.0
  <https://github.com/docker/cli/blob/master/LICENSE>

These licenses are compatible with the MIT license under which the
repository’s own source code is distributed.
